metadata.description: 10-minute walk from JR Omiko station, 8-minute walk to the nearest beach of Lake Biwa.From the building you can see Lake Biwa. You are also welcome to stay with pets!　You can live a local life without worrying like a hotel, a hotel or a group of glamping houses.Fibre optic internet, wifi throughout the building, playroom and work desk, large TV with terrestrial waves and on-demand TV are also available.

Miyagawacho Samurai Machiya is a two-level traditional "Kyo Machiya” townhouse built toward the end of the nineteenth century. It has been fully renovated and features luxurious modern facilities while preserving the original design and feel.
